What is HTML
The HyperText Markup Language or HTML is the standard markup language it is html is the skeleton of the website

What is CSS
Cascading Style Sheets is a style sheet language used for describing the presentation of a document written in a markup language such as HTML or XML.

Why did Javascript came into the picture
to provide functionality to website

History of Javascript and Ecmascript. Explain your own words.
JavaScript was invented by Brendan Eich in 1995. It was developed for Netscape 2, and became the ECMA-262 standard in 1997. After Netscape 
handed JavaScript over to ECMA, the Mozilla foundation continued to develop JavaScript for the Firefox browser.